<B>__{aaron}
<A>__{he is walking through the scrub and brush grass, every sense alive and straining. he pauses every three or four strides casting each quadrant in turn. once he whips, gun ready, as a sage hen or quail whirrs up not far from him. he smiles grimly as he watches it fly away. he keeps on.}
